  "texts": [
    "We find that incorporating contextual information significantly improves accuracy.",
    "This highlights the importance of gathering external evidence during automated verification.",
    "We find that the models show good average accuracy, but they struggle with ambiguous verdicts.",
    "Our evaluation shows that GPT-4 significantly outperforms GPT-3.5 at fact-checking claims.",
    "However, performance varies substantially across languages."
  ]
